; Coverage test for post.cc lines related to commodityless amounts
; Tests get_commodity returning empty commodity for amounts without commodity.
; Also tests get_has_cost returning false
; has_cost format expression.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    100
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format='%(commodity(amount))%(has_cost) %(account)\n'
false Expenses:Food
false Assets:Cash
end test
